%F A007531 a(n) = 6*A000292(n-2).
%F A007531 a(n) = Sum_{i=1..n} polygorial(3,i) where polygorial(3,i) = A028896(i-1). - Daniel Dockery (peritus(AT)gmail.com), Jun 16 2003
%F A007531 a(n) = 3*a(n-1) - 3*a(n-2) + a(n-3) + 6, n > 2. - _Zak Seidov_, Feb 09 2006
%F A007531 G.f.: 6*x^2/(1-x)^4.
%F A007531 a(-n) = -a(n+2).
%F A007531 1/6 + 3/24 + 5/60 + ... = Sum_{k>=1} (2*k-1)/(k*(k+1)*(k+2)) = 3/4. [Jolley Eq. 213]
%F A007531 a(n+1) = n^3 - n. - _Mohammad K. Azarian_, Jul 26 2007
%F A007531 E.g.f.: x^3*exp(x). - _Geoffrey Critzer_, Feb 08 2009
%F A007531 If the first 0 is eliminated, a(n) = floor(n^5/(n^2+1)). - _Gary Detlefs_, Feb 11 2010
%F A007531 1/6 + 1/24 + 1/60 + ... = Sum_{n>=1} 1/(n*(n+1)*(n+2)) = 1/4. - _Mohammad K. Azarian_, Dec 29 2010
%F A007531 a(0) = 0, a(n) = a(n-1) + 3*(n-1)*(n-2). - _Jean-François Alcover_, Jan 08 2013
%F A007531 (a(n+1) - a(n))/6 = A000217(n-2) for n > 0. - _J. M. Bergot_, Jul 30 2013
%F A007531 Partial sums of A028896. - _R. J. Mathar_, Aug 28 2014
%F A007531 1/6 + 1/24 + 1/60 + ... + 1/(n*(n+1)*(n+2)) = n*(n+3)/(4*(n+1)*(n+2)). - _Christina Steffan_, Jul 20 2015
%F A007531 a(n+2)^2 = A005563(n)^3 + A005563(n)^2. - _Bruno Berselli_, May 03 2018
%F A007531 a(n)*a(n+1) + A000096(n-3)^2 = m^2 (a perfect square), m = ((a(n)+a(n+1))/2)-n. - _Ezhilarasu Velayutham_, May 21 2019
%F A007531 Sum_{n>=3} (-1)^(n+1)/a(n) = 2*log(2) - 5/4. - _Amiram Eldar_, Jul 02 2020
%F A007531 For n >= 3, (a(n) + (a(n) + (a(n) + ...)^(1/3))^(1/3))^(1/3) = n - 1. - _Paolo Xausa_, Apr 09 2022
%F A007531 a(n) = 4*a(n-1) - 6*a(n-2) + 4*a(n-3) - a(n-4), n > 6. - _Enrique Navarrete_, Oct 29 2025
